Package: scCustomize
Type: Package
Title: Custom functions for single cell analyses
Version: 0.5.0.9902
Date: 2021-09-29
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Samuel", family = "Marsh", email = "samuel.marsh@childrens.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3012-6945")),
    person(given = "Ming", family = "Tang", role = c("ctb"), email = "tangming2005@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Custom functions to modify single cell analyses in publically available packages.
                    Validated with Seurat v3.1.5 & v4.0.0 and requires Seurat > v3.1.3.
                    Has also been validated with both R3.5.X+ and R4.X.X+.
URL: https://github.com/samuel-marsh/scCustomize, https://coming_soon_vignette.com 
